pull_request.title: nginx server: update to oqs-provider 0.5.2 & config update
pull_request.body:
Updates Dockerfile to generate package for test.openquantumsafe.org:
- update oqs-provider to 0.5.2 tag
- config update: sets `keepalive_timeout 0;`: to avoid unnecessary keep-alives and close connection immediately after request is fulfilled.

Update is already deployed at test.openquantumsafe.org, fulltest.sh passes.
